canonical:
  title: 寄故鄕諸老
  author: 鄭之祥
  language: lzh
  text: 山月黑溪路江風吹戍樓角聲孤起處紅葉近中秋
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 寄故鄕諸老
  author: 鄭之祥
  language: lzh
  text: 山月黑溪路。江風吹戍樓。角聲孤起處。紅葉近中秋。
korean:
  title: 고향의 여러 노인들에게 부쳐
  author: 정지상
  language: kor
  text: |-
    산과 달은 개울 길에 어둡고
    강바람은 수루에 분다
    뿔피리 소리 외롭게 일어나는 곳
    붉은 잎은 중추에 가까이 왔네
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0220_010_0440&viewSync=OT
  footnotes: []
english:
  title: Message to the Elders of My Homeland
  author: Jung Ji-sang
  language: eng
  text: |-
    Mountain and moon darken the path by the creek,
    river wind blows across the garrison tower.
    Where the horn's cry rises up alone,
    red leaves draw near to mid-autumn.
  footnotes:
  - key: ''
    value: The garrison tower (戍樓) suggests a military outpost, likely referencing the poet's service or observation from a distant vantage point
  - key: ''
    value: Mid-autumn (中秋) marks both the season and a time of reunion in East Asian tradition, creating poignancy in this message sent from afar
